                <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
                    <p class="mb-6">Navigating insurance claims can be complex. At V General Contractors, we simplify the process for you. Our team, including certified public adjusters, works on your behalf to ensure your claim is handled efficiently and you receive the maximum compensation you're entitled to. We have a proven track record of successfully managing claims for storm, hail, and other types of roof damage.
                    </p>

                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Insurance Claim Process</h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                            </svg>
                            <span>Free initial roof inspection and damage assessment.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
